{"tid":60003,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人坐親巴士都想作嘔？","createTime":"2016-12-30T06:10:05.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-30T08:22:17.000Z","uid":33898,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"23642803d1e6c10bddeb7986396c385f7cc6bec2","tid":60003,"uid":33898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:10:05.000Z","msg":"特別係啲坐成個鐘既長途巴/機場巴<br />\n有時啲狗巴仲有陣好難頂既膠味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想訓又唔舒服<br />\n次次忍到落車都要坐定個人抖唔係就會嘔出嚟<br />\n但係去到外國又坐幾耐巴士都冇事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我認我坐車都嘔正粉腸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"881284d01165d66cf8261da3f548b032068626db","tid":60003,"uid":47182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:10:52.000Z","msg":"有呀 見到對面個個直頭反胃"},{"pid":"cc74c1b8833bd11fb974c1c353bc92ddbba5d506","tid":60003,"uid":7843,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:36:13.000Z","msg":"下層仲有呀婆白花油味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e28ca847f05140aaa3c6146f3576c8c2c08de666","tid":60003,"uid":21427,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:36:28.000Z","msg":"之前搭過70X 兜路兜到嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/30.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e23525e323ad273e132a916beb0aee9e2830b51","tid":60003,"uid":65239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:54:23.000Z","msg":"戈陣漂白水+膠味難頂到極<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71955cdb70efa537793c08a17b21d7ebc21d25cc","tid":60003,"uid":22949,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T06:57:28.000Z","msg":"以前坐671去觀塘返工真係會頂唔順<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/lomore_smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1caa8de72508a2617a66d8258b0ae87a9e2271f","tid":60003,"uid":10123,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-30T07:02:22.000Z","msg":"搭親車都想嘔，除左